</ul>
</div></div><div class=3D"contentPart css-12zi0x1"><h2 id=3D"how-to-calcula=
te-the-volume-of-a-truncated-cone">How to calculate the volume of a truncat=
ed cone?</h2>
<div class=3D"textBlock"><p>If you want to know how to calculate the volume=
